    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You seem to have exposed your node over the internet and bots are trying to connect to it and mine with it. Please never expose your node to `0.0.0.0`, keep it to localhost. If you need to reach it yourself from a remote machine, use SSH + port forwarding to keep it locked down. Once you allow anyone over the internet to control your node, it's wild wild west.",
